name: John Qwashi
description:
I am an honest heart that’s looking for a stable relationship. I understand it is important to lay down lasting foundations for a lasting relationship. I am not interested in games or drama.
I like getting out and checking out local talent and live concerts, here or anywhere. I enjoy movies and music for relaxation. A quiet night at home is also enjoyed and welcomed. I am open to try different activities and up for the challenge..
I consider myself to be a fairly honest and truthful person and expect the same in return; I don’t expect someone to attempt to deceive me or “play” me.
I believe that time spent apart helps keep things fresh in a relationship and makes the time we DO spend together even better. I’m not one who cheats in a relationship; one man is enough trouble ; I don’t have the time or energy to juggle 2, 3, or 4 at the same time
